box_title: How to enable Find My Device on your phone
box_description: Launch Settings. Tap Security & lock screen. Tap Device administrators. Tap Find My Device so that a checkmark appears in the checkbox. Tap the back button in the top left corner of your screen. Tap the back button again in the top left corner to return to the main Settings menu. Tap Location in the main Settings menu.
